draw_text(x,y, "One day as you wander through your underground hometown, the ground begins to shake and rumble as rocks begin to tumble down the roof of the cave. Seeking shelter you run into a small hole along the edge of the cave.")
draw_text(x,y, "Once the rampaging earthquake has subsided, you come outside to find that your only way back home has caved in. You make your way around the cave looking for a solution only to find a staircase leading up to outside.")

